Class TestDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • TestDriver

  • public class TestDriver
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a tester class to test Car class and the interfaces it implements. There is a main method and some helpers to initialize a list of cars in random order, sort the cars based on year, make, model, and mileage, and then drive the cars and re-sort. Extra Credit: Cars are stored in an ArrayList which is part of the Collections interface. Cars are also sorted using an insertion sort that I wrote. (sorry for choosing a slow sort)
